# 🔒 Password Toolkit - Streamlit Application

![Password Toolkit Banner](https://via.placeholder.com/800x200/3498db/ffffff?text=Password+Security+Toolkit)

A comprehensive toolkit for analyzing password strength, generating custom wordlists, and creating password policies with regex validation.

## Features

- 🔐 **Password Strength Analysis**  
  Realistic strength estimation using zxcvbn algorithm with crack time predictions
- 📝 **Wordlist Generator**  
  Create targeted dictionaries for security testing with leetspeak and pattern options
- 🛡️ **Password Policy Creator**  
  Generate custom password requirements with regex validation patterns
- 📱 **Modern UI**  
  Responsive design with interactive elements and visual feedback
- 📊 **Security Insights**  
  Detailed suggestions and warnings for password improvement

## Installation

1. Clone the repository:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/password-toolkit.git
cd password-toolkit

